-- Fiat’s Maserati Almost Doubled Sales in China in 2011
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-01-02T11:30:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-02/fiat-s-maserati-almost-doubled-sales-in-china-in-2011.html
Fiat SpA (F) ’s luxury unit Maserati SpA
“almost doubled” sales in  China  in 2011 to 780 units, the
company said in an e-mailed statement. China is now the second-
biggest market for Maserati worldwide, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this
story: Chiara Vasarri in Milan at  cvasarri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible
for this story:
